  "keyFeatures": [
    "Pay airtime, electricity, data, cable TV, betting, and transport bills via API",
    "Two payment modes: wallet-signed transaction (default) and direct token transfer",
    "Payments settled in USDT or USDC on the Solana blockchain",
    "Lookup endpoints to fetch valid product IDs, plans, and providers before transacting",
    "Meter validation before electricity purchases",
    "Network detection for phone-based products",
    "Full transaction history retrieval by vendor reference or transaction ID",
    "Secure secret key authentication per vendor"
  ],
